
Comment:  Which P-flag and Mask-bits to set when a player changes status...
Comment:  The higher levels inherit bits from lower.

PflagApprentice:
  NoExorcise NoSnoop NoHassle NoAlias NoZap NoSummon NoTrace NoSteal
  NoMagic NoForce TitleEdit Emote Goto;

MaskApprentice:
  NoExorcise NoSnoop NoHassle NoAlias NoZap NoSummon NoTrace NoSteal
  NoMagic NoForce TitleEdit Emote Goto;

PflagEmeriti:
  ChScore ChLevel ChMobData TimeOut Clone Load/Store ObjectEdit
  RoomEdit MflagEdit Exorcise Reset Echo Resurrect ShowUsers Stats SummonObj
  Weather Lock Peace Healall StartInvis Trace Echoall;

MaskEmeriti:
  ChScore ChLevel ChMobData TimeOut Clone Load/Store ObjectEdit
  RoomEdit MflagEdit Exorcise Reset Echo Resurrect ShowUsers Stats SummonObj
  Weather Lock Peace HealAll StartInvis Trace Echoall;

PflagWizard:
  Asmortal InterMud;

MaskWizard:
  Asmortal InterMud;

PflagSenior:
  NameRaw Zap;

MaskSenior:
  NameRaw Zap;

PflagArchWizard:
  Frob UAFInfo Snoop Heal Alias WreckDoors Syslog;

MaskArchWizard:
  Frob UAFInfo Snoop Heal Alias WreckDoors Syslog;

PflagHighArch:
  ;

MaskHighArch:
  ;

PflagDemiGod:
  Ban PflagEdit Delete Socket;

MaskDemiGod:
  Ban PflagEdit Delete Socket;

PflagHighDemi:
  Disconnect  Shutdown  Raw Crash OpenGame MayCode;

MaskHighDemi:
  Disconnect Shutdown Raw Crash OpenGame MayCode;

PflagGod:
  MaskEdit AliasPlayer;

MaskGod:
  MaskEdit AliasPlayer; 

PflagMaster:
  ;

MaskMaster:
  ;
